Feature: Create PR

  Background: User is Logged in
    When I login
      | username | password |
      | hood004  | prs      |
      | davi037  | prs      |
    Then I visit to website

@fucus
  Scenario: User can create PR
    When I click on Purchasing button
    Then API Request @getBlanket should have status code 200
    And @getBlanket response body should have status processed
    Then Click on Marketing button
    Then Open purchasing page
    Then Browser should redirect to purchasing page
    Then Fill all requaired inputs
    And save
    Then API Request @create should have status code 200
    And API Request @create should have body status 'processed' and should return data

  @VendorName
  Scenario: Create a PR_required fields validation
    When I click on Purchasing button
    Then API Request @getBlanket should have status code 200
    And @getBlanket response body should have status processed
    Then Click on Marketing button
    Then Open purchasing page
    Then Browser should redirect to purchasing page
    And save
    Then System generates the warning message 'Vendor name is required'

  @Description
  Scenario: Create a PR_required fields validation
    When I click on Purchasing button
    Then API Request @getBlanket should have status code 200
    And @getBlanket response body should have status processed
    Then Click on Marketing button
    Then Open purchasing page
    Then Browser should redirect to purchasing page
    When Fill vendor name
    And save
    Then System generates the warning message 'Description is required'

  @ItemAmount
  Scenario: Create a PR_required fields validation
    When I click on Purchasing button
    Then API Request @getBlanket should have status code 200
    And @getBlanket response body should have status processed
    Then Click on Marketing button
    Then Open purchasing page
    Then Browser should redirect to purchasing page
    When Fill vendor name
    When Fill description
    And save
    Then System generates the warning message 'Item amount is required'

  @AmountLessThan0
  Scenario: Create a PR_required fields validation
    When I click on Purchasing button
    Then API Request @getBlanket should have status code 200
    And @getBlanket response body should have status processed
    Then Click on Marketing button
    Then Open purchasing page
    Then Browser should redirect to purchasing page
    When Fill vendor name
    When Fill description
    When Fill item amount with '0'
    And save
    Then System generates the warning messages 'Item amount can't be less than or equal to 0'
